Subject: Client List maximum 200
Description:
After updating to 5.9.4.0 I can only see 200 computers
actually before I had 1300
how can i solve it?
Solution_Comment__c: Closing ticket as resolved after increasing the "Maximum no. of records returned in a report search:" value to 1500 and the "No. of records per report page:" value to 50 in the global settings.
